        I found my way in the Media team, in charge of writing articles for the daily specialized newspapers of the event, namely the 'Good Oil'. Along with my three colleagues, our jobs consisted in interviewing participants and writing stories. Auxiliary, we were also taking care of carrying a portable toilet around, which granted us the right to have our own car - a pearl when it comes to do a bit of sightseeing in the empty Victorian's bush.

